": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 748}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "猫临终前想要些什么?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "姐姐在 99 年的时候捡了一窝三只猫，两母一公，我们一直养到现在。其中一只母猫去年离家出走了再没回来，那只公猫去年掉楼下摔死了，现在只有一只母猫在家里。因为我长期在国外，最近回家探亲才发现，做为一个 16 岁高龄的猫咪，她牙都快掉光了，之前生小猫的时候还落下点病，现在看起来挺痛苦的，好几天了除了点牛奶其他什么都不吃。半夜围着厨房喵喵叫着走来走去，买了点软的好猫粮给她也不吃，但那样子又好像她想要些什么。是疼痛在折磨她，还是想吃些啥，还是想念她的小伙伴了，还是只是想我陪她玩一下？谁有经验能告诉我下她到底想要些什么？ 我不知道她还能活多久，但我过两个礼拜又要走了，妈妈会和我一起走几个月，等我们走后就只有姐姐定期来喂个食。正在考虑在我走之前让她安乐死，是不是对她最好的安排？ 写完这些都泪流满面了……"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0599f31614cc3a575d702e75fb5483ce_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/28352696"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Ik8D8y8La0rQ5EAMaBzM1MjM3NzEgzoa0pwUwADjAK0AFcggyODM1MjY5NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1704362922.772740", "card_id": "Q_637598819", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价王者荣耀 S34 赛季？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-33e9c83667afd01fc7236b576b5208bd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637598819"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik8D8y8La0rQ5EAMaCTEwMzk2Njk0OCCriM6sBjAAODJABnIJNjM3NTk4ODE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1"